	   <tr><td colspan=2>Certainly I agree that Divine aura should always be memmed.&nbsp;&nbsp;Not only do you never know when you'll need 18secs of invincibility, but also because of the huge recast time that you need to wait before it becomes useful.  Gate should be memed to your preference.  If your always bound close by, and always getting trained you should probably mem gate.  But if your in a fairly safe area creaming blues or grouped to kill blacks, you should probably go without it.  I disagree with the need to mem your best symbol spell, the courage/center/etc. line is much better and doesn't require a reagent of which you can run out.  Pre-battle buff with your AC and HP buffs.  Others to mem are of course HEAL, if you didn't think of that one, you should play another class.  Also, Ward undead line, (if needed: no nukers) strike line, (if needed: no tanks) yalup, various cures depending on the mob, stuns and root is always helpful.  Beyond that, it really goes to personal preference and situation.<br>Gedran<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
