	   <tr><td colspan=2>At lvl 27 I have Spirit Armor, GHeal, Heal, Root, Holy Might, either Dismiss Undead or Smite (depending on the situation), Gate, and Divine Aura.<br><br>I agree with the others though, no one can tell you what spells to mem. In my opinion it is all purely situational. I personally always have Gate and Divine Aura memmed....better to be safe than sorry.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>As far as buffs go, your group members will let you know when they need them, I wouldn't waste the space to have them memmed constantly. By lvl 17 you should realize you will spend a lot of time meditating and staring at your spell book....take that time to switch out your buffs for your DD or Root spells....buff your party, then switch your spells back. (As a side note, I also use this time to work on my Sense Heading since you don't have to be standing to do that!)<br><br>Good luck finding the mix that works best for you!! =)<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
