	   <tr><td colspan=2> Necromancers are afforded the spell res, but it does come at a heavy price. Each res consumes an essence emerald, which is also used for their monster lifetap or a huge mana surge.<br><br> The down side is to get this essence emerald they have cast the spell on a lvl 45+ player, which will kill the player. The player upon which it was cast cannot be res from this action. <br><br>I have seen essence emeralds go from anywhere from 1kpp to 2.5kpp. Hope this makes you feel a bit better, due to the fact we do not need a componet to res.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
