	   <tr><td colspan=2>As a cleric I found myself medding ALOT..personaly I have a soft spot now for clerics in my group and will permit them to melee in non critical periods just cause meding sucks and is sooo boring and seporates the player from at least the visual part of the game..however my point is that often a cleric gets into a rythm of just sitting at all times and foregoes his or her looting rights...this is a horrible tragic thing for everyone deserves their fair share and it is bad enough that they do get to give critters their licks..but then recive little if any reward..ugg..heh on Rallos Zek we have the luxery of actualy being able to kick someone causing them to stand up..group leaders on blue servers...I implore you to be the avocate for your cleric and make sure he/she removes his or her nose from that cursed book and takes their cut..this will not just make a happy cleric but will produce in time a cleric who doesnt mind spending a few cats eyes to symbol up the group. <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
